comments: different from other professors in a good way. she is real and very into teaching.

Dr. Murphy is not only a teacher, she is a leader. I have never worked so hard in any class but I really feel I am learning, reaching for ideas I never thought of. Her Native American centered pedagody is just the out of the box thinking I have been waiting for. Thank you Dr. Murphy for the best class of my academic career.
She is really hard but really passionate and an excellent teacher. Her life story inspired me and I leaned more in her class than any other in my two years here at Wheelock.
